duties_responsibilities.duty: Meet with merchants and present programs designed to save them money on their credit/debit card processing and equipment.
Offer a Cash Discount Program that eliminates the merchant's processing fees.
Utilize a proven sales process that is results-driven.
Receive appointments and have access to 24/7 technical and customer support for the merchant.
Never have to install equipment, and have Sales Managers available for support at every step.
